parcel.description:
Welcome to NoPoPark, a place of upmost tranquility and zen. All are welcome to contribute to the beauty of this park, including claiming booths to decorate and display wares. 

Just please pick up your trash, the locals get a little weird. 

When building, please do not change the overall layout of the scene, but feel free to add or alter anything you see besides booths that are in use and the staircase/structure.

Message @Felblob on twitter to add yourself to the contributors list or to suggest an idea for the park. A twitter feed for the park is coming soon.

-NoPoPa Bureau of Pixel Management
